  "name": "RPlog_The_Imperator_s_Coronation",
  "title": "The Imperator's Coronation",
  "summary": "Imperator Circle on Selene is remade into a festive, cosmopolitan bazaar to celebrate the coronation of Tyler Damion as Imperator of the new Imperium, the rebranded Galactic Empire. Admiral Crestian Tarasar tours the festivities with his Kubaz tailor while the embittered former CDU Presav Elana Tracer, hungover and grieving, looks on with disgust at the regime that destroyed her Caspar. Behind a communications cloak, the Imperator confers with his advisors Crestian and Grand Admiral Drayson Honos about consolidating the Caspian Democratic Union as a vassal state and enforcing anti-slavery and pro-xeno policies, then summons Tracer for a personal audience. Over an open-air luncheon, Malign and Crestian engage Tracer in a philosophical sparring match about freedom, the death of her old Caspar, and the deaths of her enemies by Malign's own hand, before the Imperator offers her a governorship over Corporate Sector worlds. Tracer, wary but intrigued and desperate to see her son Kipran before his deployment, agrees to consider the proposal, and Malign delays the deployment two days and leaves her in Crestian's hands.",
